Title: Phase of a chiral determinant and global SU(2) anomaly
Authors: A. A. Slavnov
Comments: 6 pages, Latex, no figures
Report-no: SMI-15-97
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B415 (1997) 390-394
\\
  A representation for the phase of a chiral determinant in terms of a path
integral of a local action is constructed. This representation is used to
modify the action of chiral SU(2) fermions removing the global anomaly.
